NOTICE
======

This repository redistributes XML materials from the CBETA project.

Original Source
---------------

CBETA — Chinese Buddhist Electronic Text Association
財團法人佛教電子佛典基金會

Official repository:
https://github.com/cbeta-org/xml-p5

The files contained in the `xml-p5` directory are unmodified redistributions
of CBETA XML TEI P5 files. All original CBETA headers are preserved.

License and Usage Condition
---------------------------

CBETA permits redistribution of its XML corpus for NON-COMMERCIAL use,
provided that the full CBETA header remains intact in each file.

This repository complies with that requirement.

All users of this repository must:

- Preserve the original CBETA headers in every file
- Maintain non-commercial use of the CBETA materials
- Respect CBETA’s ownership of the original texts

Translations
------------

The English translations in the `xml-p5t` directory are collaborative
derivative works based on CBETA XML files.

They are distributed under the same non-commercial condition
as the original CBETA materials.

Independence
------------

This project is an independent translation effort and is not an official
CBETA publication.

If CBETA requests changes regarding attribution or redistribution,
the repository maintainers will comply accordingly.
